    <div class="content">
    <h2>Objective</h2>
    Explore the playfield while avoiding clicking on mines.
    <br/>
    <br/>
    <h2>Flags</h2>
    Right click, or shift-click a tile to mark it with a flag
    <br/>
    <br/>
    <h2>Scoring</h2>
    <div class="clear"></div>
    <br/>
    Each tile revealed: <span class="right">1 point</span>
    <br/>
